    "description": "【公司规模】1000-9999人\n【行业】房地产业\n【地址】耀华路251号\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.8em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【企业标签</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px;line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世界</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">500强3</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">位</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">国有企业</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】【</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">上市公司</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">精品先锋</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】【</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">“鲁班奖”全国同类企业之最</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">中共</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">一大纪念馆</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】【</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">迪士尼城堡</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">中国馆</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px;line-height: 1.8em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">和谐为本，追求卓越】【</span><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">连续</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">八</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">年上海第一</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></p><p style=\";line-height: 1.8em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\";line-height: 1.8em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【薪酬福利</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></strong></p><p style=\";line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【本科首年收入</span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">8～</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">8</span></strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">W</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></p><p style=\";line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【绩效奖金】【项目兑现】【现场津贴】【值班津贴】</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">补充公积金</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】【补充商业医疗险】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">定向培养</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></p><p style=\";line-height: 1.8em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">【人才公寓】【项目住宿】【免费午餐】【技能培训】</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:always\"/></span> </p><p style=\"line-height: 1.8em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">【应聘方式</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">】</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">1、企业</span><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">唯一</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">招聘邮箱</span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 16px\">：</span><strong><span style=\";font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,255);font-size:19px\">hush5264@scc4.cn</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（邮件标题请注明：校名</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">+专业+姓名+应聘岗位</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2、企业宣讲会（综合招聘会）：现场请携带个人简历、成绩单、获奖证书复印件等；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3、第三方平台：可登入前程无忧（51JOB）及各高校就业信息网进行在线应聘。</span></p><p><br/></p>",
