    "description": "【公司规模】500-999人\n【行业】信息传输、软件和信息技术服务业\n【地址】浦东新区顾唐路1899号银联数据大楼\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 根据工作需要，按照公开招聘有关政策规定，现启动2026年度校园招聘。欢迎有梦想、有才华的你加入银联数据！</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">一、单位简介</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">银联数据服务有限公司（简称银联数据）是中国领先的账户服务商，于2003年在上海成立，是中国银联的控股子公司。国家规划布局内重点软件企业。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">目前，银联数据已为国内外众多发卡机构提供了包括银行卡发卡核心系统、消费信贷数据服务系统、增值服务系统和数据分析服务在内的专业化解决方案，并不断向泛金融、政务、科技、文旅等多行业、多领域拓展。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">二、招聘计划</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">本次校园招聘共涉及2个职位5人，具体岗位资格及有关条件详见附件《2026年校园招聘职位列表》或公司官方招聘网站（官网地址：https://cupdata.zhiye.com/）。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">三、招聘对象</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">2025年1月至2026年12月期间毕业且为初次就业的境内外院校大学本科及以上学历应届毕业生（不含定向生、委培生），能如期毕业并取得学历学位证书。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">四、简历投递</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">请应聘人员登录我公司官网投递简历（官网地址：https://cupdata.zhiye.com/），投递时间为自公告发布之日起至4月23日，每人最多投递1个职位。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei UI\">应聘资格、应聘流程、注意事项等详细信息请登录我司官网查阅。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>",
